lt_.               1. Let _fraction_ be the string-concatenation of CodePointsToString(_parsedFraction_) and *&#34;000000000&#34;*.               1. Let _nanosecondsString_ be the substring of _fraction_ from 1 to 10.               1. Let _nanoseconds_ be ℝ(StringToNumber(_nanosecondsString_)).             1. Return _sign_ × (((_hours_ × 60 + _minutes_) × 60 + _seconds_) × 10&lt;sup&gt;9&lt;/sup&gt; + _nanoseconds_).           ">
